Package: ehrcplot
Title: MAKING GGPLOT GRAPHICS IN EHRC STYLE
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Paul", "Smith", , "paul.smith@equalityhumanrights.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Helps create and export ggplot2 charts in the style used by the EHRC
        data team thanks to two useful functions, one for styling and another for exporting
        ggplot graphics. Build using bbcplot (https://github.com/bbc/bbplot), with thanks.
URL: https://github.com/pws3141/ehrcplot/
BugReports: https://github.com/pws3141/ehrcplot/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    png,
    grid,
    ggpubr,
    dplyr,
    data.table
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
